57:50.717 --> 57:51.717
Neither do I.

57:51.760 --> 57:52.840
Both: Me, neither.

57:52.928 --> 57:53.928
Let's see.

57:55.180 --> 57:57.546
Colonel mustard in the study,

57:58.141 --> 57:59.141
