58:11.571 --> 58:13.311
Good night, honey.
Good night, north.

58:13.407 --> 58:15.819
- Good night.
- Night, mom. Night, dad.

58:15.909 --> 58:17.991
Brush your teeth
before you go to bed.

58:23.917 --> 58:25.782
Sorry to bother you
at this late hour,

58:25.877 --> 58:28.117
