01:07:21.663 --> 01:07:22.994
No reason.

01:07:23.915 --> 01:07:25.075
Ah! Ah!

01:07:37.303 --> 01:07:38.418
Ah!

01:07:51.818 --> 01:07:53.354
We won't see him no more.

01:08:48.625 --> 01:08:50.707
Watch, watch, watch!
